{"tid":1469051,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對818既一項建議","createTime":"2019-08-14T00:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:57.000Z","uid":206617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6028d5bdfd90c2ab86e5b74b91c2b376562ed0fb","tid":1469051,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:18:55.000Z","msg":"呢篇係以現時需要勇武中場休息+和理非抗爭為中心既一個建議方安<br />\n<br />\n睇之前，建議先睇以下內容：<br />\n吳志森：咁落去，呢場運動會輸 而且輸得好甘！（分析＋建議，請入黎睇睇）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460980</a><br />\n轉發:一名政府人員的看法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462190</a><br />\n公務員黃絲老豆話：「林鄭已經透露咗......」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464380</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥呢排話要俾啲時間政府<br />\n而呢排好多風都係吹事後有獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n所以我係到建議一件事：<br />\n既然話林鄭話完左呢件事後就&ldquo;修補&rdquo;社會關係<br />\n咁我地應該係818 要求林鄭係828之前向公眾提交&ldquo;修補時間表&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中場休息，重啟 DEADLINE </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求提交時間表</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要佢用時間表去回應我地既訴求<br />\n如果較&ldquo;遲到既公義&rdquo;都俾唔到我地，我地就更有理據去升級我地既行動<br />\n而呢個時間表，亦係俾中間派別人士去睇下政府有冇心去解決當前問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但</span></strong></span><br />\n如果個時間表冇委員會，冇政改<br />\n中途仲要拉人，咁當我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d8075dfcf22d2b2effd27ea1891302b616c4d3","tid":1469051,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:22:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd154aef5073ec1145cf4609c31d82845146e68","tid":1469051,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0deeb9984e5dfda943116373159036b3d11c71b7","tid":1469051,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:37:49.000Z","msg":"推呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff34a1d7cb3073868826d057b774240ee350d44","tid":1469051,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:52:14.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5e87180ecae185937f35045bcb960ac391e84fbb","tid":1469051,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:54:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb7388fbe8478d8162a335849c5d675c603005aa","tid":1469051,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:00:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7fa2603cdf5f5bca22938a605677964882cd6ea","tid":1469051,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:06:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfafff2955113d97d53c70052cc48ef6f95759ff","tid":1469051,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:18:11.000Z","msg":"pack"},{"pid":"6ef4922b1f1b6c70407f7a0960cb27591a64b69d","tid":1469051,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:30:12.0